name: Enter Reason for Out Duty

testSteps.description: 1: Enter Reason for Out Duty ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=Apply, tab=Out Duty/Tour, fromDate=31/10/2022, toDate=31/10/2022, outOfDutyType=Out Duty (Client Visit), enterReason=client visit})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "Apply" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
When User clicks on "Out Duty/Tour" Tab
Then Select "31/10/2022" From date and "31/10/2022" till Leave dates for Out Duty Tour
And Select "Out Duty (Client Visit)" from Type dropdown
Then Enter "client visit" in "outing Reason" text box
